{"parentUuid":"e4ee4e16-084f-486b-921f-b0be5095dbf1","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"c027074d-043d-4986-a6bf-3d4493c3ee80","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_00_ot3YbEHaHbfsYGsP7FlCnXYH","type":"tool_result","content":"D盘剩余空�? 117.8 GB\n\n=== AppData\\Local 大文件夹 ===\n  360Chrome: 1151 MB\n  Application Data: 20608 MB\n  Doubao: 752 MB\n  google: 2720 MB\n  JianyingPro: 7479 MB\n  kingsoft: 2623 MB\n  Microsoft: 1023 MB\n  Sogou: 614 MB\n  Tencent: 510 MB\n\n=== AppData\\Roaming 大文件夹 ===\n  Accio: 971 MB\n  DingTalk: 2239 MB\n  kingsoft: 6540 MB\n  KuGou8: 1280 MB\n  SodaMusic: 1314 MB\n  Tencent: 4952 MB","is_error":false}]},"uuid":"008914c1-72ca-4c92-ae22-23030a2da6b3","timestamp":"2026-04-24T01:42:59.922Z","toolUseResult":{"stdout":"D盘剩余空�? 117.8 GB\n\n=== AppData\\Local 大文件夹 ===\n  360Chrome: 1151 MB\n  Application Data: 20608 MB\n  Doubao: 752 MB\n  google: 2720 MB\n  JianyingPro: 7479 MB\n  kingsoft: 2623 MB\n  Microsoft: 1023 MB\n  Sogou: 614 MB\n  Tencent: 510 MB\n\n=== AppData\\Roaming 大文件夹 ===\n  Accio: 971 MB\n  DingTalk: 2239 MB\n  kingsoft: 6540 MB\n  KuGou8: 1280 MB\n  SodaMusic: 1314 MB\n  Tencent: 4952 MB","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"e4ee4e16-084f-486b-921f-b0be5095dbf1","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"c7e06c6a-8029-4d8b-86ad-964b61b73a7b","version":"2.1.118","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
{"parentUuid":"008914c1-72ca-4c92-ae22-23030a2da6b3","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"100190a9-0d32-4f68-978b-de33b3820952","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-reasoner","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Very interesting! After my cleanup, here's what's still big in AppData:\n\n**Local:**\n- Application Data: 20,608 MB (20.6 GB!) - This is very suspicious. In modern Windows, \"Application Data\" in Local is usually a junction point/symlink to Roaming. Let me check what this actually is - it might be a directory junction or something unexpected.\n- JianyingPro (剪映): 7,479 MB (7.5 GB)\n- kingsoft (WPS): 2,623 MB (2.6 GB)\n- google (Chrome): 2,720 MB (2.7 GB)\n- 360Chrome: 1,151 MB (1.1 GB)\n- Microsoft: 1,023 MB (1 GB)\n- Doubao: 752 MB\n- Sogou: 614 MB\n- Tencent: 510 MB\n\n**Roaming:**\n- kingsoft (WPS): 6,540 MB (6.5 GB)\n- Tencent (微信/QQ等): 4,952 MB (4.9 GB)\n- DingTalk (钉钉): 2,239 MB (2.2 GB)\n- SodaMusic: 1,314 MB (1.3 GB)\n- KuGou8 (酷狗): 1,280 MB (1.3 GB)\n- Accio: 971 MB\n\nThat \"Application Data\" at 20.6 GB is very suspicious. In Windows, `C:\\Users\\Administrator\\AppData\\Local\\Application Data` is typically a reparse point (junction) pointing to `C:\\Users\\Administrator\\AppData\\Roaming`. If we count it separately, it's double-counting files already in Roaming. Let me check this.\n\nSo the actual space usage that can be addressed:\n\n1. **JianyingPro (剪映) - 7.5 GB** - Cache files, can be cleaned in-app or safely deleted (caches auto-rebuild)\n2. **WPS/kingsoft - 2.6 + 6.5 = 9.1 GB** - WPS Office files, can be moved/cached\n3. **Tencent (微信/QQ) - 0.5 + 4.9 = 5.4 GB** - Can change storage path in app settings\n4. **Chrome - 2.7 GB** - Can clear cache or move profile\n5. **DingTalk - 2.2 GB** - Can clear cache in-app\n6. **Doubao - 752 MB** - Cache\n7. **360Chrome - 1.1 GB** - Can clear cache\n8. **Kugou/SodaMusic - ~2.6 GB** - Music cache, can be cleaned in-app\n9. **Accio - 971 MB** - Cache\n\nSo AppData currently probably has about 30+ GB that could be addressed.\n\nNow, to answer the user's question: \"为什么不能移，没有办法吗\"\n\nThere are several approaches:\n\n### 1. Symbolic Links / Junction Points (高级方法)\nYou can move an AppData folder to D: drive and create a symbolic link at the original location. Windows and apps will think it's still on C: drive.\n\n**How**: \n```cmd\n# Step 1: Move the folder\nmove \"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\AppData\\Local\\JianyingPro\" \"D:\\AppDataLinks\\JianyingPro\"\n# Step 2: Create junction point\nmklink /J \"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\AppData\\Local\\JianyingPro\" \"D:\\AppDataLinks\\JianyingPro\"\n```\n\n**Risks**:\n- Some apps don't follow junctions properly\n- Windows updates may break symlinks\n- If D: drive fails, apps break\n- Some antivirus flag symlinks suspiciously\n\n### 2. Change app-internal storage paths (推荐)\nMany apps let you change where they store data:\n- **微信/WeChat**: Settings → File Management → Change storage path to D:\n- **QQ**: Settings → File Management → Change path to D:\n- **Chrome**: Can change download path, but profile path is harder to change\n- **WPS**: Can change backup/autosave path\n- **JianyingPro (剪映)**: Can clear cache in app settings\n\n### 3. Clear app caches (安全)\nMost app caches can be safely cleared without affecting functionality:\n- JianyingPro cache\n- Chrome cache\n- WPS backup cache\n- Doubao cache\n- Music app caches\n\nLet me present this to the user in a helpful way.","signature":"100190a9-0d32-4f68-978b-de33b3820952"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":449,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":61056,"output_tokens":1555,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"a5490889-db7f-4557-a36b-201c0aa8ee07","timestamp":"2026-04-24T01:43:12.296Z","use